<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h2 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-bottom: 20px;">You've been invited to join Survivor Draft!</h2>
        
        <p style="color: #34495e; line-height: 1.6;">
          You've been invited to join Season <%= @draft.season_number %> of Survivor Draft.
        </p>
        
        <p style="color: #34495e; line-height: 1.6;">
          The draft will start on <%= @draft.airing_datetime.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %> and will include <%= @draft.episodes_count %> episodes.
        </p>
        
        <div style="margin: 20px 0;">
          <%= link_to 'Join Draft', @invite_url, 
              style: "display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #3498db; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
        </div>
        
        <p style="color: #34495e; line-height: 1.6;">
          If you don't have an account yet, you'll need to create one to join the draft.
        </p>
        
        <p style="color: #34495e; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 20px;">Best regards,<br>The Survivor Draft Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html> 